summary: 该插件用于检测Confluence应用的多个漏洞，包括CVE-2021-26084代码执行漏洞、CVE-2015-8399信息泄露漏洞以及CVE-2021-26085任意文件读取漏洞。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect multiple vulnerabilities in the Confluence application, including CVE-2021-26084 Remote Code Execution, CVE-2015-8399 Information Disclosure, and CVE-2021-26085 Arbitrary File Read vulnerabilities.
